{"tid":2484571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何超蓮與男友「女上男下」","createTime":"2021-04-11T16:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T11:42:05.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ebdb85c6f004ad38610085447b71ac0f4005d151","tid":2484571,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:08:52.000Z","msg":"賭王三房千金何超蓮與大陸男星竇驍自公開戀情以來，都表現得非常恩愛。富家女超蓮甘願為男友下廚，竇驍亦相當識做，會陪女友做運動，而且難度愈做愈高！<br />\n<br />\n他們經常邊拍片邊做運動，上載社交平台與網友分享，最近他們玩「女上男下」掌上壓，超蓮於男友背上做掌上壓，竇驍下盤超穩陣，完全沒有手騰腳震，一看就知訓練有素。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20210411/photo/0411-00282-011b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210411%2Fphoto%2F0411-00282-011b1.jpg&h=0154cf42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1025b837f9949e22de6c40b6583b1a3ce217ebd","tid":2484571,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:43:25.000Z","msg":"好以比超蓮後入<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea4e1ad966eb7aa6b9b12098d13c6b2c849f64c","tid":2484571,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T21:27:28.000Z","msg":"多情真係麻撚煩<br />\n又失戀多一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f95f5d35cd3f453e83dadcf0a42442ce7bf91d","tid":2484571,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T21:30:27.000Z","msg":"咁好條件都要俾大陸仔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517a5e24cb0ec5249889a7bab4fb8b1ca52003e2","tid":2484571,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"問到腳味 😂"},{"pid":"a43f2a896dc7fa2d99aee41338cf17bd324e2ec2","tid":2484571,"uid":22554,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a7f95f5d35cd3f453e83dadcf0a42442ce7bf91d","tid":2484571,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T21:30:27.000Z","msg